 explains key characteristics of observed flare hard\nX-ray spectra as well as the underlying properties of the accelerated\nparticles. Our analytic model provides tools to interpret high-energy\nobservations for missions and telescopes, such as RHESSI, FOXSI, NuSTAR, Solar\nOrbiter, EOVSA, and future high-energy missions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Jan 2022 17:14:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-16"}
