the first\ntime that block coordinate descent methods have been developed and analyzed for\npolicy optimization in reinforcement learning, which provides a new perspective\non solving large-scale RL problems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 15 Jan 2022 04:42:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Feb 2022 22:41:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 17 Sep 2022 04:17:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-20"}
